  "remarks": "JSC All-Russian Scientific Research Institute “Gradient” is a Russian military industry company. It produces radio-technical equipment. JSC All-Russian Scientific Research Institute “Gradient” is a developer of Krasukha-4 multifunctional mobile radio-electronic suppression REP complex that is used by Russian armed forces in the war of aggression against Ukraine.",
